      "content": "look i'm not trying to be difficult but i really cant make it to a clinic right now. its just a bit of tightness. i have some old prednisone tablets in my cabinet from a previous flare up... if i just take one of those along with my usual inhaler will that help clear out the inflammation so i can sleep? it feels like it should work since it's the same medicine.",
